    <item>
      <title>英特尔首席执行官基辛格退休，股价大幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/intel-ceo-gelsinger-retires-stock-rises-sharply-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司首席执行官帕特·基辛格已从公司退休并辞去董事会职务，而此时公司正试图实施扭亏为盈计划。受此消息影响，该公司股价大幅上涨。Jonathan Ferro 和 Lisa Abramowicz 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/intel-ceo-gelsinger-retires-stock-rises-sharply-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:01:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
