    <item>
      <title>本周全球大宗商品值得关注的五大关键图表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球对美国玉米的需求正在攀升。作为全球最大的电线金属供应国，美国的铜产量在连年下滑后正在回升。而中国电动汽车的繁荣有可能削弱汽油需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
